review_title: For Dry Skin, or Dry Climate
review_content:
Only for Dry Skin; does NOT work on my combination skin. It just slides around, doesn't settle in (and I'm not even greasy right now); after a while my cheeks just look blotchy. For dry skin I would definitely recommend it, because the peachy Papaya tint has a great girly natural looking flush color, nice texture, and smells like bubble gum. Taking off 1 star ONLY because the product description did not mention that this is geared towards dry skin type.
